# Ecosystem QA governance

NurseNest QA must validate **one cohesive premium adaptive clinical ecosystem**, not disconnected products.

## When changing learner/marketing surfaces

1. Map tests to `docs/governance/ecosystem-qa-master-program.md`.  
2. Prefer extending existing Playwright specs over one-off checks.  
3. Copy report templates from `docs/governance/ecosystem-qa-report-templates/` into `reports/ecosystem-audit/` after major releases.

## Quick commands (from `nursenest-core/`)

- `npm run test:e2e:ecosystem-audit` — curated homepage + hubs + learner smoke  
- `npm run qa:release-gate` — deploy gate  
- `npm run qa:ecosystem:matrix` — print full command matrix  

